Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.27,0:17:05.73,insert_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Welcome to Rock'n Roll Fight
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.73,0:17:07.56,insert_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}I'm just a Rock'n Roll MAN
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.69,0:17:09.96,insert_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}We're just a Rock'n Roll BAND
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.04,0:17:16.39,insert_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}俺達は道なりに　走り続けて来た
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.43,0:17:21.70,insert_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}標識だらけの道を　とばし続けていく
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.73,0:17:27.02,insert_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}幾つもの町を抜け　歌い続けて来た
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.28,0:17:32.42,insert_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}腑抜け野郎共を　煽り続けていく
