Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.04,0:17:16.39,insert_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我們沿著大道一路跑來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.43,0:17:21.70,insert_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}飛過那標誌林立的街角
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.73,0:17:27.02,insert_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}伴著歌聲穿越無數城畿
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.28,0:17:32.42,insert_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}煽動起這一眾窩囊混帳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.70,0:17:39.44,insert_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}漫長的寒冬冰雪融盡 烈風肆意席捲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.57,0:17:44.52,insert_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}今時今日 烈風依舊肆虐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.46,0:22:16.02,ed_jp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}全てがもし
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.05,0:22:19.69,ed_jp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}決められてたら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.98,0:22:28.71,ed_jp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}僕らはどうして　もがくのだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.02,0:22:32.87,ed_jp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}それは、君じゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.93,0:22:36.57,ed_jp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}君の、せいじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.60,0:22:44.06,ed_jp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}悲しみはもうたくさんなんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.29,0:22:47.91,ed_jp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}だから、そうじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.06,0:22:51.84,ed_jp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}今の、ままじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.93,0:22:59.51,ed_jp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}うまく伝えきれないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.57,0:23:06.92,ed_jp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}DEAR MY FUTURE
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.17,0:23:15.86,ed_jp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}DEAR YOUR FUTURE
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.11,0:24:04.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.46,0:22:16.02,ed_cn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}如果這一切
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.05,0:22:19.69,ed_cn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}早已命中注定
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.98,0:22:28.71,ed_cn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}那我們又為何 仍在苦苦掙扎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.02,0:22:32.87,ed_cn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}其實那 與你無關
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.93,0:22:36.57,ed_cn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}你並沒有 做錯什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.60,0:22:44.06,ed_cn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}悲傷已經足夠多了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.29,0:22:47.91,ed_cn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}因此 並不是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.06,0:22:51.84,ed_cn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}並不是 現在這個樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.93,0:22:59.51,ed_cn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}只是無法將心情傳達給你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.57,0:23:06.92,ed_cn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}DEAR MY FUTURE
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.17,0:23:15.86,ed_cn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}DEAR YOUR FUTURE
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.94,0:23:29.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個奇跡般的力量 是需要付出代價的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.59,0:23:31.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這你能明白嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.92,0:23:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我還是會做的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.49,0:23:34.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了陽毬
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.87,0:23:38.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,生存戰略 邪門歪道隨時奉陪

